message.content: cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.COMM, cs.SY - The paper discusses a new hybrid spectrum access scheme for mmWave networks, which involves scheduling data packets through two mmWave carriers with different characteristics. This involves aspects of network infrastructure (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), millimeter wave technology (cs.MM), communication systems (cs.COMM), and system engineering (cs.SY).
